com.team1389.hardware

Class Hardware<T extends PortInstance>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1389.hardware.Hardware<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the hardware port type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompositeWatchable, Watchable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CANTalonHardware, FlashlightHardware, GyroHardware, PDPHardware, PotentiometerHardware, ServoHardware, SolenoidHardware, SwitchHardware, Victor888Hardware, VictorHardware

    public abstract class Hardware<T extends PortInstance>
extends java.lang.Object
implements CompositeWatchable
    wraps a WPI lib hardware object, adding watchable support and port tracking via Registry

    Subclasses are intended to handle the case where the hardware fails to claim a port on construction

    Author:
    amind
